**TL;DR** :

Langflow is a visual, low-code platform built on top of LangChain, designed for creating AI applications, including multi-agent and RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) apps. It provides a drag-and-drop interface, enabling developers to quickly prototype and build AI workflows without extensive coding. Langflow is open-source, Python-based, and fully customizable, offering a flexible and intuitive environment for building AI solutions.
